37:24.563 --> 37:25.404
He was a big wheeled maniac.

37:25.424 --> 37:25.564
Uh-huh.

37:25.584 --> 37:26.125
So I kind of modified that.

37:26.145 --> 37:29.911
When I interviewed Colin Freyburn in Oxford, England, you may know, he's quite an important deal.

37:29.931 --> 37:30.031
Sure.

